The story is set in the eastern mountain range of the Durrowen Valley, North of Mt Hrvet. The Settlers come from the early Igston Empire, their ancestors believing in the Estelithean values. The settlements purpose was to start a new, and to eventually set up a trade route as a network through the northern reaches of the empire into the Durrowen valley.
They settled in a beautiful plains surrounded by forests of rolling hills. The mountains surround the settlement. A river runs nearby down a series of valleys into Durrowen.
A series of ruins are scattered throughout the landscape. Waiting for the settlers to uncover.
The settlements town is Meljoir.
